de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.winter.model

Class Correspondence<RecordType extends Matchable,CausalType extends Matchable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.winter.model.Correspondence<RecordType,CausalType>
  • Type Parameters:
    RecordType -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Correspondence<RecordType extends Matchable,CausalType extends Matchable>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represent a correspondence. Contains two Records and their similarity score. May also contain causal correspondences that explain how this correspondence was created (correspondence provenance)
    Author:
    Oliver Lehmberg (oli@dwslab.de)
    See Also:
